Pink Floyd
From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
Jump to navigationJump to search
Pink Floyd
A black-and-white photo of five men standing in front of a brick wall.
Pink Floyd in January 1968, from the only known photoshoot of all five members. Clockwise from bottom: Gilmour, Mason, Barrett, Waters and Wright.
Background information
Origin	London, England
Genres	
Rockpsychedelicprogressive rock
Years active	
1965â€“199520052012â€“2014
Labels	
EMI ColumbiaTowerHarvestCapitolColumbiaSony MusicEMIParlophone
