The above albums were reissued on CD in 1987, followed by the 1988 compilations Past Masters â€“ Volume One and Past Masters â€“ Volume Two, which collected all of the Beatles' non-album singles plus the 1964 EP Long Tall Sally and a few other rarities that were commercially available in the 1960s.

